ABOUT THE FAIR

Cosmoscow International Contemporary Art Fair is a highly anticipated art festival that aims to unite the art scene’s indisputable trendsetters: galleries, artists, experts, art collectors and connoisseurs from Russia and all over the world.

Since 2014 Cosmoscow has taken place every September, establishing its own place in the international art calendar. The latest edition of the fair took place at Gostiny Dvor on September 11-13, 2020, representing 67 Russian and international galleries and welcoming nearly 9600 guests.
